# Contributing

Thanks for helping improve **Awesome AI SEO & GEO Tools**.

This repository is meant to be a useful, neutral, and practical resource for people working on AI SEO, Generative Engine Optimization, llms.txt, structured data, multilingual SEO, technical SEO, and answer-engine visibility.

## What You Can Suggest

You can suggest:

- AI SEO tools
- GEO tools
- llms.txt tools
- Schema.org and structured data tools
- Hreflang and international SEO tools
- Technical SEO validators
- Sitemap and robots.txt tools
- AI search analytics tools
- Learning resources
- Browser extensions
- Open-source SEO tools

## Content Guidelines

Please keep submissions:

- Useful
- Relevant
- Clear
- Non-promotional
- Short
- Publicly accessible

Avoid:

- Keyword stuffing
- Long promotional copy
- Affiliate links
- Duplicate tools
- Tools with unclear purpose
- Broken or inaccessible URLs

## Listing Format

Use this format:

```markdown
- [Tool Name](https://example.com/) - One short sentence explaining what the tool helps users do.

Good Example
- [Schema Markup Validator](https://validator.schema.org/) - Validate Schema.org structured data across different markup types.

Bad Example
- [Best SEO Tool Ever](https://example.com/) - The most powerful and best platform that guarantees ranking and traffic growth.
